query:
INSERT INTO
                vm_runner_bwip (
                    l1_batch_number,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at,
                    processing_started_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, NOW(), NOW(), NOW()) ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
                updated_at = NOW(),
                processing_started_at = NOW()
